            <title><![CDATA[【#不良情绪易诱发癌症# 一起保持好情绪[心]】#不良情绪对身体有哪些影响# 惊恐会使我们身体的气机运行出现紊乱，严重时会影响先天之本从而导致生病；思虑会出现...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%98%93%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%98%93%E8%AF%B1%E5%8F%91%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不良情绪易诱发癌症#</span></a> 一起保持好情绪<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/l_xin-43af9086c0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E5%AF%B9%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E5%AF%B9%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E6%9C%89%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不良情绪对身体有哪些影响#</span></a> 惊恐会使我们身体的气机运行出现紊乱，严重时会影响先天之本从而导致生病；思虑会出现气机郁结，特别容易影响脾胃运化，如果出现气血不足、痰浊内生，就会导致免疫力下降，从而患病。专家提示，情绪是癌症的一大诱因。如何预防不良情绪对身体的影响，专家总结了一个顺口溜，详戳👇🏻 <a href="http://t.cn/A6Nupkhx" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
